Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Bekehrung Pauli" addressed to "Technische Hochschule Darmstadt z. Hd. V. Herrn Prof. Dr. H. G. Evers 6100 Darmstadt" and dated 09.09.1966

  • Extracts from different publications about the 'Conversion of Saint Paul'
  • Bibliographic references

The inventory of 1993 also mentions black and white reproductions, but these are missing and were probably taken out in the Rubenianum and filed in the Rubens documentation.
